name: Sinisistar nun（white/black clothes）
description:
This is a Lora model for the nun character in Sinisistar1. I used 60 to 50 images to train it.

The trigger words are sinisistarblack, sinisistarwhite, and nsfw.

I used the NAI model as the base, and ran the images at 768x1024 resolution, so the Lora effect is much better than before…and it can have very high generality and so on, even scared me…I didn’t expect that this thing runs better on 2D than 2.5D, and 2.5D runs better than real human models…

There is one more thing, the weights are probably between 0.6 and 1, because I set the learning rate relatively low, 3e-5/3e-5/5e-6, so you can directly pull the Lora weights to relatively high…(even if it is 1 it seems to be okay?)

There is one more thing, because there is some trigger word pollution, please add some descriptive words manually, such as white hair flower, white dress and so on, otherwise you may have a situation where you write sinisistarwhite and get a black nun clothes…

Also, because I used 768x1024 resolution, this model has better effect on this resolution or similar long images like 512x768, and may not perform well on 768x512 or 512x512 images(0v0)

The nsfw of this model is usually tentacles, even if you don’t add tentacles Lora, the tentacles it shows are very sexy…(laugh)

:)

(ps: I didn’t add the r18g cg content from the game, thank you! I don’t hate r18g and similar works, just personally can’t accept it physically, bye bye)

关于Sinisistar1里的修女角色的lora，用了60到50张图训练

触发词分别为sinisistarblack，sinisistarwhite，nsfw

然后是在NAI模型上使用的，跑的图片是768x1024，所以比之前的lora效果好多了.....而且可以有非常高的通用性什么的，甚至把我自己给吓到了.....这玩意跑二次元比2.5d好，2.5d比跑真人模型好是我没想到的.....

还有一件事，权重大概在0.6到1，因为我的学习率调的比较低，3e-5/3e-5/5e-6,所以lora的权重你可以直接拉到比较高.....（哪怕是1也好像没关系？）

还有一件事，由于存在一定的触发词污染，请人为加上一些描述词，比如white hair flower，white dress之类的，不然可能会有你写了个sinisistarwhite出来个black nun clothes的情况......

另外，我因为使用的是768x1024，所以该模型对这样的分辨率或者512x768以及类似的长条图的效果比较好，对768x512或者512x512可能效果比不了什么的（0v0）

这个模型的nsfw一般为触手，哪怕你不加触手lora，它表现出来的触手也是非常的涩......(笑)

：）

（ps：我没加游戏里的r18g的cg内容，谢谢！我不讨厌r18g以及类似作品，只是个人生理有点接受不能，溜了溜了）

pixiv账号：https://www.pixiv.net/users/19252533
